---
/**
 * @component Beneficios.astro
 * @description Sección que resalta las ventajas competitivas de la empresa (Atención rápida, Certificados INDECI, etc.).
 * Refactorizado a Tailwind CSS para Electrion.
 */
---

<section class="py-16 text-center bg-electrion-dark border-y border-white/10">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-12 text-white drop-shadow-md">
      ¿Por qué elegir a ELECTRION?
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      <div
        class="p-6 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-[0_10px_25px_rgba(0,0,0,0.2)] hover:border-electrion-accent hover:bg-white/10 group"
      >
        <span
          class="text-5xl block mb-4 drop-shadow-md group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
          >⚡</span
        >
        <h3 class="text-white text-xl font-bold mb-3">Atención Rápida</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-sm">
          En Moquegua, Ilo y alrededores. Llegamos antes de que se descongele tu
          refri.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="p-6 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-[0_10px_25px_rgba(0,0,0,0.2)] hover:border-electrion-accent hover:bg-white/10 group"
      >
        <span
          class="text-5xl block mb-4 drop-shadow-md group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
          >📜</span
        >
        <h3 class="text-white text-xl font-bold mb-3">Certificados INDECI</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-sm">
          Firmados por ingenieros colegiados. Garantizamos que pasas la
          inspección sin problemas.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="p-6 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-[0_10px_25px_rgba(0,0,0,0.2)] hover:border-electrion-accent hover:bg-white/10 group"
      >
        <span
          class="text-5xl block mb-4 drop-shadow-md group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
          >💳</span
        >
        <h3 class="text-white text-xl font-bold mb-3">Pago Fácil</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-sm">
          Aceptamos efectivo, Yape, Plin y transferencias. Emitimos Factura
          estructurada o Boleta.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="p-6 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-[0_10px_25px_rgba(0,0,0,0.2)] hover:border-electrion-accent hover:bg-white/10 group"
      >
        <span
          class="text-5xl block mb-4 drop-shadow-md group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
          >🛡️</span
        >
        <h3 class="text-white text-xl font-bold mb-3">Garantía Real</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-sm">
          No desaparecemos. Si algo falla, volvemos y lo arreglamos sin costo
          adicional para ti.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
